    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Create a fire in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Ceramic Ferro Rod Micro Striker. This tiny fire starter survival tool is easy to carry and possibly the simplest, wearable edc gear that has a useful intended purpose while being completely out of the way when fashioned into a zipper pull or fire starter necklace using 550 paracord. Easily start a camp fire with one good scratch from this ceramic fire striker by creating sparks against a ferro rod or magnesium. Unlike traditional fire steel that can corrode with oxidation or rust if it gets wet and not cared for. This lightweight emergency fire starter is made from extremely hard zirconia ceramic material that will continuously create sparks without absorbing heat; it will not dull, wear out or rust</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Ceramic Micro Striker Scraper Emergency Fire Starter</h2>\n  <p>Create a fire in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Ceramic Ferro Rod Micro Striker. This tiny fire starter survival tool is easy to carry and possibly the simplest, wearable edc gear that has a useful intended purpose while being completely out of the way when fashioned into a zipper pull or fire starter necklace using 550 paracord.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>EMERGENCY FIRE STARTER - Designed to never fail you when you must build a fire to survival, this ferro rod and magnesium scraper can be used thousands of times</li>\n    <li>LIGHTWEIGHT SURVIVAL EDC - Built from Zirconia Ceramic this emergency fire starter striker is super hard (Like Diamond); will never dull, rust or wear out</li>\n    <li>CAMPING GEAR ACCESSORY - Fashion on 550 paracord as a zipper pull, fire starter necklace, or key ring for easy access</li>\n    <li>EMERGENCY SURVIVAL KIT - Pair together with a ferro rod and magnesium to create a lightweight EDC camping survival kit</li>\n    <li>Will not absorb heat created from sparks; continuously scrape out hot sparks until you get your fire started</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/survival_kits/CMS_micro_striker_ASR_2pk_detail_02.jpg\" alt=\"Create a fire in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Ceramic Ferro Rod Micro Striker\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROCMSS</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886397335</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Easily start a camp fire with one good scratch from this ceramic fire striker by creating sparks against a ferro rod or magnesium. Unlike traditional fire steel that can corrode with oxidation or rust if it gets wet and not cared for. This lightweight emergency fire starter is made from extremely hard zirconia ceramic material that will continuously create sparks without absorbing heat; it will not dull, wear out or rust. It will produce a shower of super-hot sparks capable of igniting almost any tinder in most all conditions, wet, damp or dry.</p>\n  <p>Weighing next to nothing and taking up very little room in your hiking backpack proves the ASR Outdoor fire striker is a must have camping survival tool for your wilderness survival kit creating endless sparks from ferrocerium or for shaving and scraping magnesium. Effective fire starting must start with a spark and this is a top priority while prepping for emergency survival.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
